{"tid":2065984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被吳重儀惡意還押小欖教師周四高院申請保釋","createTime":"2020-06-16T03:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T02:59:00.000Z","uid":246828,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"30dc28d546453e711f9003b4489acebc01148d43","tid":2065984,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%B0%8F%E6%AC%96-%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E5%90%91%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%25AC%2596-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%2590%2591%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7k9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=cbdc439a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%25AC%2596-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%2590%2591%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&h=16f1a335\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%B0%8F%E6%AC%96-%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E5%90%91%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n//小學男教師楊博文於去年 11 月 11 月「黎明行動」及「三罷」期間，在上水迴旋處被質疑慢駛，遭警方截查時被指腳踢警長。經審訊後，楊在上周五（12 日）被裁定襲警罪成，主審裁判官吳重儀稱，關心他心智是否有問題，押後至 6 月 26 日判刑，以索取精神、心理及背景等報告，期間將他還押小欖精神病治療中心。據悉，楊博文將於本周四（18 日）向高等法院申請保釋等候判刑。<br />\n<br />\n29 歲被告楊博文，本身是小學教師，亦是沙灘排球港隊代表。他被控於去年 11 月 11 日，在上水掃管埔路迴旋處襲擊正在執行職責的警長。楊於上周五曾向裁判官吳重儀申請保釋，惟裁判官稱楊已被定罪，襲警勢必判監，拒絕其申請。<br />\n<br />\n辯方曾作求情，希望裁判官可以考慮被告無預謀、警員無受傷，重犯機會小，加上被告將來仍想教書，如判以監禁之後不能繼續當教師，希望裁判官判以非監禁刑罰。裁判官聽取求情後，質疑被告心智有問題，「心智可唔可以繼續教書？想知佢精神心智有無問題？」又批評他為人師表「守法意識薄弱，阻塞交通自私自利、衝動狂妄、犯錯不遵指示，無悔意」，遂將案件押至 6 月 26 日判刑，以索取兩份精神科報告、心理及背景報告，期間要被告還押小欖精神病治療中心。//"},{"pid":"98534e7b924b20298b5e39dad134a6398d2dec8d","tid":2065984,"uid":246828,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ikSzEqx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FikSzEqx.png&h=5404ba8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af2a7dfea3fa969cdd35f939a56e1e7c5dd00a9a","tid":2065984,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:29:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b314b20a979731a24fd1d84f6fe1ae056755459","tid":2065984,"uid":83328,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uQq13TG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuQq13TG.png&h=4bda34e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飯都食唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97266ba232659bc1503498589641c94e209082e2","tid":2065984,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:33:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裁判官聽取求情後，質疑被告心智有問題，「心智可唔可以繼續教書？想知佢精神心智有無問題？」</blockquote><br />\n認同啊 普羅大眾都質疑緊你心智有問題 大家都「想知你精神心智有無問題」咁幾時到你判自己入去小欖住返排檢查吓心智同精神狀況? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29061ba94bfe3c4bbc7415700aa0ffaad31ddccc","tid":2065984,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b90e335911a30c74443fde61a19bb3c07e0314","tid":2065984,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b314b20a979731a24fd1d84f6fe1ae056755459","t